reviewText: Was a favorite in our house years ago. Purchased for my grandchildren and now another generation is enjoying it.
All 3 of my kids watched as they where growing up, and they all loved it. Great songs and characters, I love Eureeka's Castle!
I was very happy with the product I received.  The picutre and soung were of very good quality.  It was also shipped very quickly

I was disappointed with the quality of this vhs. I know it was pretty old and I have received others where the jackets were worn but the product inside was good. This vhs jumped very badly in places. I realized it was used, but expected it to be in better condition for the money.
